dmca.title: Lay Off Our Buch&Bilde
dmca.body:
Dear [private],

You are the webmaster of aaron.cyberfreakout.com.

On your site there are information about the Unimog.

It is illegal to publish or copy the original Unimog literature, because there is a copyright.

We demand you to cancel these datas immediately:

Service Manual
Engine Parts Manual
Chassis Parts Manual
Lubrication Chart
24 Volt to 12 Volt Converter
Printer


Otherwise we have to contact DaimlerChrysler and our lawyer. If you
don't follow our instructions, we have to claim compensation from you, because we have the copyright for these literature since 1994.

Please contact us ([private]@buchundbild.de).



Sincerely,

[private]
www.Buch&Bild.de



Unimog Literature
Buch&Bild
[private]
www.buchundbild.de
Germany

fax + 49 [private]
